        "mainbody": "'''Vilheim Baltson''' was a native of [[Chessenta]]. He was a paladin of [[Torm]] when, during the [[Time of Troubles]], he lost connection with his god, (when Torm was killed by [[Bane]] in [[Tantras]]). Feeling abandoned, he retreated to the [[Great Glacier]] to live as hermit. However, in [[1366 DR|1366]], he agreed to help the [[Harper]] [[Martine]] in fighting the [[Ice devil]] [[Vreesar]]."
